snippet.description:
Im so sorry it was hard to see

 CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY RELAYED BY NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE AUSTIN/SAN ANTONIO TX 647 PM CDT WED JUN 10 2020 

THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY. THIS IS A CHILD ABDUCTION ALERT ISSUED BY THE TEXAS AMBER ALERT NETWORK THE MATHIS POLICE DEPARTMENT IS SEARCHING FOR ENRIQUE HERNANDEZ, HISPANIC, MALE, 5 YEARS OLD, HEIGHT 3 FEET 11 INCHES, WEIGHT 80 POUNDS, BROWN HAIR, AND BROWN EYES. POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR STEPHANIE OLIVAREZ, HISPANIC, FEMALE, 22 YEARS OLD, HEIGHT 5 FEET 6 INCHES, WEIGHT 223 POUNDS, BROWN HAIR, AND BROWN EYES, IN CONNECTION WITH HIS ABDUCTION. THE SUSPECT IS DRIVING A RED, 2002, DODGE, NEON WITH A TX, LICENSE PLATE NUMBER OF L D R 8 4 2 1. THE SUSPECT WAS LAST HEARD FROM IN MATHIS, TX. LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THIS CHILD TO BE IN GRAVE OR IMMEDIATE DANGER. IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE MATHIS POLICE DEPARTMENT AT 361 547-2113. NEWS MEDIA POINT OF CONTACT IS MATHIS POLICE DEPARTMENT AT 361 547-2113. $$
